## Provider Versioning

### Version Constraint

```hcl
terraform {
  required_providers {
    oci = {
      source  = "oracle/oci"
      version = ">= 5.0.0, < 6.0.0"
    }
  }
}
```

### Version Operators

| Operator | Meaning |
|----------|--------|
| = 1.0.0 | Exactly version |
| >= 1.0.0 | Greater or equal |
| <= 1.0.0 | Less or equal |
| ~> 1.0 | 1.x range |
| >= 1.0.0, < 2.0.0 | Range |

### Upgrade Provider

```bash
# Upgrade
terraform init -upgrade

# Pin specific version
terraform {
  required_providers {
    oci = {
      source  = "oracle/oci"
      version = "5.26.0"
    }
  }
}
```

### Best Practice

- Pin version em production
- Test before upgrade
